<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>보험료 계산하기</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/directH1.css">
<script src="../../js/jquery/jquery-1.8.3.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/ui.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/ui_common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<div id="skipNavi"><a href="#h1Wrap">본문 바로가기</a></div>
<header>
	<h1>보험료 계산하기</h1>
	<a href="#none" class="btnHome">메인으로 이동</a>
	<a href="#none" class="btnInfo">1</a>
</header>

<!-- content -->
<div id="h1Wrap">
	<div class="driverVisual">
		<p>
			<strong>손해를 예방하는<br>현대해상 운전자 보험</strong>
			<span>자동차보험 가입 고객님께 <em>초회보험료 12%</em> 더 할인!</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<section class="section02">
		<form>
			<fieldset>
				<legend>정보입력</legend>
				<div class="inputWrap">
					<input type="text" id="name" required />
					<label for="name">이름</label>
				</div>
				<div class="inputWrap two">
					<input type="tel" id="number01" required>
					<label for="number01">주민등록번호<em class="hide">앞자리</em></label>
					<input type="password" placeholder="●●●●●●●" id="number02" />
					<label for="number02" class="hide">주민등록번호뒷자리</label>
				</div>
				<div class="inputWrap">
					<input type="tel" id="phone" required />
					<label for="phone">본인명의 휴대폰번호('-없이')</label>
				</div>
			</fieldset>
		</form>
		<ul class="listDot">
			<li>최근 계산 내역이 있을 경우 이름, 주민등록번호, 휴대폰 번호입력하여 내역 확인 후 보험료 계산을 이어서 진행할 수 있습니다.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<div class="btnWrap two">
		<span><a href="#" role="button">최근 계산 내역</a></span>
		<span><a href="#" role="button">보험료 계산하기</a></span>
	</div><!-- //style -->
	<!-- //content -->
</div>
</body>
</html>

